#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.63:0.2"
msgid "7. Ekadhammapeyyālavagga"
msgstr "7. Abbreviated Texts on One Thing"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.63:0.3"
msgid "63. Kalyāṇamittasutta"
msgstr "63. Good Friends (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.33"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.63:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.63:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Ekadhammo, bhikkhave, bahūpakāro ariyassa aṭṭhaṅgikassa maggassa uppādāya."
msgstr "“Mendicants, one thing helps give rise to the noble eightfold path."

msgctxt "sn45.63:1.3"
msgid "Katamo ekadhammo?"
msgstr "What one thing?"

msgctxt "sn45.63:1.4"
msgid "Yadidaṃ—kalyāṇamittatā."
msgstr "It’s good friendship."

msgctxt "sn45.63:1.5"
msgid ""
"Kalyāṇamittassetaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ "
"maggaṃ bhāvessati, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarissati."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with good friends can expect to develop and cultivate the noble "
"eightfold path."

msgctxt "sn45.63:1.6"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti, "
"ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant with good friends develop and cultivate the noble "
"eightfold path?"

msgctxt "sn45.63:1.7"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ "
"nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti "
"vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, "
"right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right "
"immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as "
"letting go."

msgctxt "sn45.63:1.8"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti, "
"ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant with good friends develops and cultivates the noble "
"eightfold path.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.63:1.9"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
